title: Two Sides to Every Date: " Established 1999"
description: Christian is wondering what went wrong with his date with Hailey because she's not being super responsive and he thinks it's because he took an important phone call during the date.  When Hailey tells us what it is, you'll probably laugh but what you'll really find hilarious is what the phone call was about that Christian took.
